          "reviewBody": "The school management is very poor in academic coordination. All the positive reviews are posted by the teachers teaching in the school. Each one are assigned daily to post positive reviews to get ratings in all the platforms.\nThe curriculum followed by them is too tough for the children's to understand. Students are taught like guinea pigs. No exposure or anything for students. The fee structure is too high and what they provide is not upto the amount we pay.\nThe working atmosphere is highly toxic. Internal politics are played well and faculties are targeted when they object certain decisions made by the school authorities. The staffs salary are been hold and deducted purposefully stating illogical reasons. The teachers are rotationally changed every year. Every year many faculties are resigned and new faculties are appointed with less experience. Teachers are tortured and no relaxations are given to them. If you want to enjoy job and family this institution is not recommended. Comparing to other schools this school only gives less holidays and teachers are not allowed to take leave under any emergency. Even staffs are forced to work during public holidays. We all work hard for the wellbeing of the family but here family comes second. Teachers don't get time to spend with their family and thus with lack of holidays and relaxation teachers are exhausted. This institution is a pakka corporate.",
